Class StandardAtomicHIOA_Factory

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.AbstractAtomicModelFactory
      • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.StandardAtomicModelFactory
        • fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models.StandardAtomicHIOA_Factory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AtomicModelFactoryI, java.io.Serializable

    public class StandardAtomicHIOA_Factory
extends StandardAtomicModelFactory
    The class StandardAtomicHIOA_Factory defines a basic factory used when the instantiation protocol of an atomic HIOA model class does not modify the one defined in the class AtomicHIOA.
